import React from 'react'
import { Sidebarcontainer, Icon, Closeicon } from './sidebarelement'

const Sidebar = () => {
    return (
        <Sidebarcontainer>
            <Icon>
                <Closeicon></Closeicon>
            </Icon>
            <Sidebarwrapper>
                <Sidebarmenu>
                    <Sidebarlink to='about'>
                    
                    </Sidebarlink>
                </Sidebarmenu>
            </Sidebarwrapper>
        </Sidebarcontainer>
    )
}

export default Sidebar
